Kelly Preston -LRB- born October 13 , 1962 -RRB- is an American actress and former model .
She has appeared in more than sixty television and film productions , most notably including Mischief , Twins and Jerry Maguire .
She is married to John Travolta , with whom she collaborated on the fantasy film Battlefield Earth .
She also starred in the films The Cat in the Hat , Old Dogs , and Broken Bridges .